title: Step2 Little Baker's Kitchen
description: Compact, upscale and colorful kitchen for little chefs!

asset.author: Step2
asset.description: Compact, upscale and colorful kitchen for little chefs!

transcripts: The perfect toy for aspiring chefs who want to cook up some fun. The Little Baker's Kitchen from Step2 provides kids with the ability to prepare their own food toy goodies and to clean up too. Complete with a stove, fridge, sink, storage shelves, dish-rack, microwave, and recycle bin. This fully equipped kitchen is almost as the real thing and much better if you're too short to reach the real life counters. Little one's love the variety of built in accessories like the doll seat and the granite look counter tops. The realistic electronic stove burner has provided hours of entertainment in our house with it's special pot and frying pans that trigger sizzling and bubbling noises from the stove. The little baker kitchen is sure to cook up plenty of fun.
